                    <sic>dont</sic> think his means sufficient<lb/> to accomplish his object. If it
                    lay'<sic>s</sic> in your power to<lb/> assist him <sic>trough</sic> your
                influence, it will in my <sic>judgement</sic><lb/> be a great <add>Hebrew</add>. He
                has toiled and labored hard this six<lb/> years and was never able to maintain his
                familyâ€”so it is<lb/> best for him to return with his wife &amp; child to his
                home.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I have not received and not seen the Occident from<lb/> last month
                yetâ€”no other subscriber here received any.<lb/> Why?</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Before <add>Hebrew</add> you will receive nearly (if not all)<lb/>
